---
title: Southwest Turkey & Cauliflower Rice with Poblano & Smoky Red Pepper Crema
description: Cauliflower rice is one of those ingredients that makes you feel healthy, while also being incredibly delicious. Our chefs took cauliflower rice for tonight’s Southwest-inspired meal and layered it with Tex-Mex-seasoned ground turkey. They tossed in sautéed poblano and onion for good measure (and even more veggies). With a drizzle of smoky red crema and a sprinkle of cilantro all over, this “rice” is extra nice.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/southwest-turkey-cauliflower-rice-a47c6166.jpg
